des:
Keeping your diabetes under control will help you prevent heart, nerve, and foot problems. 

You can ask me about your daily questions like:

Is it ok to drink alcohol?
How does diabetes impact my menstrual cycle ?

This is meant for educational purpose only. Please refer to a Medical Practitioner for any medication advice.
